{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1702-07a_50","head":{"value":"[Paraphrase]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juillet 1702 [première partie] [tome 9], p. 50-57.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Mr l’Abbé Anselme, si celebre par ses excellentes Predications, a fait en Latin l’Epitaphe du Roy d’Angleterre Jacques II. &amp; tous ceux qui l’ont lûë, l’ont admirée. Mr le Ch. G. en a fait la Paraphrase, &amp; l’on y a trouvé des beautez qui ne vous échaperons pas.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"value":"PARAPHRASE DE L’EPITAPHE DU ROY D’ANGLETERRE.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":[{"l":[" Regi Regum, felicique Memoriæ","Jacobi II. Majoris Britanniæ Regis."]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au Roy qui fais regner tous les Rois de la terre,","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et pour transmettre aux siecles à venir","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le precieux dépost de l’heureux souvenir","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[3]/#"},"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du grand Roy","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Jacques","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"d’Angleterre.","id":"/div/quote/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[2]/#"}}]}]},{"l":[" Qui sua hîc viscera condi voluit,","Conditus Ipse in visceribus Christi."]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce lieu saint, est l’azile, ainsi qu’il l’a prescrit,","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ses Entrailles venerables :","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et lui-même goûte le fruit,","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ses vertus incomparables,","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans l’azile éternel du sein de","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[4]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Jesus-Christ.","id":"/div/quote/lg[3]/l[4]/hi[1]/#"}}]}]},{"l":["Fortitudine bellicâ nulli secundus,"," Fide Christianâ cui non par ?"]},{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[5]/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nul ne porta plus haut la gloire","id":"/div/quote/lg[5]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[5]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui suit la parfaite valeur ;","id":"/div/quote/lg[5]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et par la pure Foi qui regna dans son cœur,","id":"/div/quote/lg[5]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A qui ne peut-on pas comparer sa memoire ?","id":"/div/quote/lg[5]/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":[" Per alteram quid non ausus ?","Propter alteram quid non passus ?"]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est-il quelque chemin aux grandes actions","id":"/div/quote/lg[7]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où ne l’ait pas conduit l’ardeur de son courage ?","id":"/div/quote/lg[7]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est-il de coup affreux de revolutions","id":"/div/quote/lg[7]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui de sa Pieté n’ait esté le partage ?","id":"/div/quote/lg[7]/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":["Illâ plusquam Heros,"," Istâ propè Martyr."]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il remplit d’un Heros les plus vastes desirs","id":"/div/quote/lg[9]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tandis qu’il fut guidé par sa vertu morale :","id":"/div/quote/lg[9]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans ce qu’il souffrit, sa Foi fut presque égale","id":"/div/quote/lg[9]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[9]/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A la Foi même des Martyrs.","id":"/div/quote/lg[9]/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":["Fide fortis, accensus periculis,"," Erectus adversis."]},{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fort de cette force sublime,","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son cœur sans relâche agité","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parut dans les perils toûjours plus magnanime,","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et plus grand dans l’adversité.","id":"/div/quote/lg[11]/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":[" Nemo Rex magis cui Regna quatuor,","Anglia, Scotia, Hibernia. Ubi quarum ?","  Ipse sibi."]},{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vraiment grand Roi ! dont le pouvoir suprême","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eut quatre Empire sous ses loix ;","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Angleterre, &amp; l’Ecosse, &amp; l’Irlande à la fois ;","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et quel estoit quatriéme ?","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Celui qui le rendit sage entre les grands Rois,","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’empire qu’il eut sur soi-même.","id":"/div/quote/lg[13]/l[5]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":["Tria eripi potuere, Quartum intactum mansit.","Priorum defensio Exercitus, qui defecerunt,","Postremi tutela Virtutes, nunquam transfugæ."]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des trois premiers sans peine on a pû le priver,","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lorsqu’on vit ses Troupes rebelles,","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Loin de perir pour les sauver,","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pousser leurs attentats jusqu’à se soulever ;","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais du dernier les Gardes immortelles","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ses Vertus, dans la paix sçeurent le conserver,","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et luy furent toûjours fidelles.","id":"/div/quote/lg[15]/l[6]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":[" Quin nec illa tria erepta omninò.","Instat Regnorum est Ludovicus hospes.","Sarcit amicitia talis tantæ sacrilegia perfidiæ."," Imperat adhuc qui sic exulat."]},{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Encor ceux-là, quoy qu’envahis,","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne luy furent pas même entierement ravis :","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans son cœur, malgré la sacrilege audace","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De tant de crimes inoüis,","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[4]/#"},"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Hospitalité de","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[4]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Louis","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[4]/hi[1]/#"}}]},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Remplit abondamment la place","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des droits sacrez du Trône indignement trahis.","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les augustes liens d’une amitié si forte","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans la grandeur Royale ont soutenu ses jours :","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[9]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Estre exilé de la sorte","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[10]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’est-ce pas regner toûjours ?","id":"/div/quote/lg[17]/l[10]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":["Moritur, ut vixit, Fide plenus,","Eòque advolat, quò Fides ducit,"," Ubi nihil perfidia potest."]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin sa vive Foy sanctifia sa vie,","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Consomma par sa mort sa tendre Pieté,","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’enleva dans la felicité,","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":"  ","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De nostre celeste Patrie,","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Inaccessible aux traits de l’Infidelité.","id":"/div/quote/lg[19]/l[4]/hi/#"}}}]},{"l":["Non fletibus hîc, Canticis locus est,"," Aut si flendum, flenda Anglia."]},{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de Cantiques saints ce Tombeau retentisse,","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que toûjours on en bannisse","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les larmes &amp; les douleurs :","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou s’il y faut pleurer, s’il faut qu’on y gemisse,","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour l’Angleterre seule, il faut verser des pleurs.","id":"/div/quote/lg[21]/l[4]/hi/#"}}}]}]}}}